        "text": "And they shall turn away their ears from the truth - That is, the people themselves will turn away from the truth. It does not mean that the teachers would turn them away by the influence of their instructions.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And shall be turned unto fables; - See the notes at 1 Timothy 1:4. ",
